=== β_m^{orb} = (m-3)/2 ANALYSIS ===

Values:
  m=3, p=7: β_m^orb = 0
  m=5, p=11: β_m^orb = 1
  m=7, p=15: β_m^orb = 2
  m=9, p=19: β_m^orb = 3
  m=11, p=23: β_m^orb = 4
  m=13, p=27: β_m^orb = 5
  m=15, p=31: β_m^orb = 6
  m=17, p=35: β_m^orb = 7
  m=19, p=39: β_m^orb = 8

This is:
  β_m^orb = (m-3)/2 = (p-7)/4
  β_m = m*(m-3)/2
  β_{m+1} = m*(m-3)/2 + (p-1) = m*(m-3)/2 + 2m = m*(m+1)/2 = C(m+1,2)

